#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_potions/commands.lua:11
msgid ""
"<effect>|heal|list|clear|remove <duration|heal-amount|effect>|INF [<level>] "
"[<factor>] [NOPART]"
msgstr ""
"<效果> | 治疗 | 列表 | 清除 | 移除 <持续时间 | 治疗量 | 效果> | 无限 [<等级"
">] [<系数>] [无粒子效果]"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_potions/commands.lua:12
msgid ""
"Add a status effect to yourself. Arguments: <effect>: name of status effect. "
"Passing \"list\" as effect name lists available effects. Passing \"heal\" as "
"effect name heals (or harms) by amount designed by the next parameter. "
"Passing \"clear\" as effect name removes all effects. Passing \"remove\" as "
"effect name removes the effect named by the next parameter. <duration>: "
"duration in seconds. Passing \"INF\" as duration makes the effect infinite. "
"(<heal-amount>: amount of healing when the effect is \"heal\", passing a "
"negative value subtracts health. <effect>: name of a status effect to be "
"removed when using \"remove\" as the previous parameter.) <level>: effect "
"power determinant, bigger level results in more powerful effect for effects "
"that depend on the level (no changes for other effects), defaults to 1, pass "
"F to use low-level factor instead. <factor>: effect strength modifier, can "
"mean different things depending on the effect, no changes for effects that "
"do not depend on level/factor. NOPART at the end means no particles will be "
"shown for this effect."
msgstr ""
"给自己添加一个状态效果。参数说明如下：<效果>：状态效果的名称。若将“列表”作为"
"效果名称传入，则会列出可用的效果。若将“治疗”作为效果名称传入，会按照下一个参"
"数所设定的数值进行治疗（或造成伤害）。若将“清除”作为效果名称传入，则会移除所"
"有效果。若将“移除”作为效果名称传入，会移除由下一个参数所指定名称的效果。<持续"
"时间>：以秒为单位的持续时长。若将“无限”作为持续时间传入，则该效果会变为永久性"
"的。（<治疗量>：当效果为“治疗”时的治疗量，传入负值则会扣除生命值。<效果>：当"
"先前参数使用“移除”时，此处为要移除的状态效果的名称。）<等级>：效果强度的决定"
"因素，对于那些依赖等级的效果而言，等级越高，效果越强（对于其他效果则无变"
"化），默认值为1，传入“F”则改为使用低级系数。<系数>：效果强度修正值，其具体含"
"义因效果而异，对于不依赖等级/系数的效果则无变化。末尾的“无粒子效果”表示该效果"
"不会显示粒子效果。"

